	* gonzui/bdbdbm.rb (Gonzui::BDBExtension::tail): Removed.
	(Gonzui::BDBDBM::initialize): Use BDB::INIT_CDB instead of
	BDB::INIT_LOCK. 
	(Gonzui::BDBExtension::delete_both): Use BDB::WRITECURSOR.

