	pkgid_fmtids and pkgid_lcsids. 

	* gonzui/config.rb (Gonzui::Config::initialize): Change the
	default DB cache size to 1MB.

	* gonzui/dbm.rb (Gonzui::IDCounter::flush): Fix a bug. Update
	"seq" DB correctly.

