	AutoPack.pack_id2.
	* gonzui/deindexer.rb (Gonzui::Deindexer::deindex_content): Use
	AutoPack.pack_id2. 

	* gonzui/dbm.rb (Gonzui::AbstractDBM::close): Call flush_cache.

